"6\"><b>An Example: the `sum` function</b></font>\n\n* Custom R approach\n```{r sumR}\nsumR <- function(x) {\n  \n  total <- 0\n  for (i in 1:length(x)) {\n    total <- total + x[i]\n  }\n  \n  return(total)\n}\n\nsumR(x)\n```\n\n----\n\n<font size=\"6\"><b>An Example: the `sum` function</b></font>\n\n* `Rcpp` approach\n```{r sumC}\nlibrary(Rcpp)\n\ncppFunction('double sumC(NumericVector x) {\n            \n  int n = x.size();\n  double total = 0;\n  for(int i = 0; i < n; ++i) {\n    total += x[i];\n  }\n  \n  return total;\n}')\n\nsumC(x)\n```\n\n----\n\n<font size=\"6\"><b>An Example: the `sum` function</b></font>\n\nSpeed test: \n\n```{r speed_test}\nlibrary(microbenchmark)\n\nmicrobenchmark(sum(x), sumR(x), sumC(x), times = 1000L)\n```\n\n----\n\n<center>\n  <img src=\"http://www.edii.uclm.es/~useR-2013/pics/grouph.jpg\" alt=\"group_image\" width=\"800\">\n  Thank you for your attention!\n</center>\n",
